1. We convert the three txt file datasets into their respective json files by using the 
      Sarcasm_tweets.txt ----> tweets_txt_to_json.py ----> Sarcasm_tweets.json
      Sarcasm_tweets_with_language.txt ----> tweets_with_lang_to_json.py ----> Sarcasm_tweets_with_language.json
      Sarcasm_tweet_truth.txt ----> tweets_stance_to_json.py ----> Sarcasm_tweet_truth.json

