2. Now we join all the json files using the joining_json.py
3. We treat the "label" key of json file as a ClassLabel type using the reading_json.py and also we add another key called "id_str"
    its value is same as that of key "id" but it's a string unlike of "id"
4. Now we push the final json file into the Hugging Face Repository using the final_json_push_tohub.py